  _aiDescription: "Mid-range unit with slightly higher stats than a Warrior.\n\nAt the start of each round, throws a spear forward to hit the enemy frontline, then fights as a regular mid-range unit.\n\nBalance: 3 Spearmen ≈ 5 Warriors.\n\nPlacement: use center lane X = 0 as the primary/default Spearman position. Then fill X = -2 and X = 2. Use side lanes X = -4 / 4 only from Wave 13+ when more Spearmen are needed."
